# tui-gif tape — tour of every top-level tab. Useful as a sanity-check GIF
# proving the binary launches and every screen renders.
#
# Run:  go run ./cmd/tui-gif vhs/tui-gif/screens-tour.tape

Width 144
Height 44
Delay 350ms
Output vhs/out/screens-tour.gif

Key 1
Sleep 500ms
Key 2
Sleep 500ms
Key 3
Sleep 500ms
Key 4
Sleep 500ms
Key 5
Sleep 500ms
Key 6
Sleep 500ms
Key 7
Sleep 500ms
Key 8
Sleep 500ms
Key 9
Sleep 500ms
Key 0
Sleep 700ms

# Back to dashboard.
Key 1
Sleep 600ms
